# 📅 Calendar Reminder Helper & iPhone Alarm Automation

This project helps you get **reliable reminders on iPhone** by:

✅ Creating *helper events* in Google Calendar at your reminder times using a Google Apps Script.
✅ Using an iPhone Shortcut to set **native iOS alarms** based on these helper events.

Perfect for ensuring alarms even when Google Calendar notifications are unreliable on iOS.

